# Code Sample üíª

```java
WebDriver driver = new ChromeDriver();
driver.get("https://google.com");
WebElement element = driver.findElement(By.name("q"));
element.sendKeys("Selenium Testing");
element.submit();
driver.quit();
```

# Multi-window ü™ü

```java
String originalWindow = driver.getWindowHandle();
for (String handle : driver.getWindowHandles()) {
    driver.switchTo().window(handle);
}
```

Selenium makes it easy to switch between tabs and popups.

# Complex Moves üñ±Ô∏è

For drag-and-drop, double-click, or hover:

```java
Actions actions = new Actions(driver);
actions.moveToElement(element).click().perform();
```

# Secret Sauce üíâ

Sometimes you need to run JS directly in the browser to scroll or bypass issues.

```java
JavascriptExecutor js = (JavascriptExecutor) driver;
js.executeScript("window.scrollBy(0,250)");
```

# Visual Evidence üì∏

```java
File srcFile = ((TakesScreenshot)driver).getScreenshotAs(OutputType.FILE);
FileUtils.copyFile(srcFile, new File("failure.png"));
```

